snippet.title: EZ TALK LIVE   Amber Nicole Smith Chilling Story
snippet.description:
Subscribe to http://ezwaynetwork.com

Amber Nicole Smith supported by actor comedian Kat Williams and his wife has a chilling story to tell. First time heard only on EZ TALK LIVE on eZWay Network's http://eZWay.TV

Amber talks about how she was rapped and forced into sex trafficking and the same time being a mother with a unfortunate death in regards to her son. YET SHE STILL KEEPS HER HEAD HIGH and wants to tell her story to inspire other mothers and everyone that comes anywhere close to walking the path she has walked. 

Show episode hosted by Eric Zuley
Intro produced by: Dante Sears and Eric Zuley

National and international syndication: iLaunchezway.com Twiggitv.com, WomenOnTV, Roku, Apple TV, Amazon Fire TV, Voice America, WBCF, WXFL Alabama channels, KLXA, FANTV LA, and more...
